Mary Schuyler won the 72-ounce steak dinner challenge at the Big Texan Steak Ranch restaurant in Amarillo, Texas on Sunday . 
  The 120-pound mother-of-four broke the record for quickest steak dinner eaten and earned $6,000 in prize money . 
  She ate three steaks, three shrimp cocktails, three baked potatoes and three salads in just 20 minutes . 
  She beat the previous record of four minutes and 18 seconds set last year . 
 